The paper deals with learning-based techniques for geometric processing of non-rigid shapes, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of neural networks and deep learning also suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
